ast.name: github
ast.comment:
Provides common functionality for managing bugs, milestones, and other functionality on GitHub.

Operations are limited to GET and POST methods due to platform limitations at this time.

decls.name: app
decls.comment: Custom application name. The module name is the default and will be appended to a custom name.
